description: A bride was making a magical entrance at her wedding on a grand staircase with her dad escorting her, when a woman dashed past and slid down the marble railing at the Free Library of Philadelphia. That woman was the bride's wedding planner.
title: Bride And Groom Speak Out After Wedding Slide Video Goes Viral #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: Sean Saifa Wall from Atlanta is candid about his journey to discovering and living as a person who is intersex. He was castrated and put on feminizing hormones as a teen, but didn't realize the extent of having androgen insensitivity syndrome until he was in college. Since his discovery, he's worked tirelessly to find his place in the world and advocate for intersex awareness. "That's why I continue to do this work," he told Inside Edition Digital's Andrea Swindall.
title: Man Turns Personal Intersex Journey Into Fight for Awareness
